---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy" description="xConvert24.com cookie policy — understand what cookies we use, why, and how to manage them." keywords="cookie policy, cookies, tracking, Google Analytics cookies, manage cookies, GDPR cookies">
  <div class="max-w-3xl prose dark:prose-invert prose-gray">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2025</p>

    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      This page explains how xConvert24.com uses cookies and similar technologies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Cookies are small text files stored on your device by your web browser. They help websites remember information about your visit.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Cookies We Use</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <thead class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Cookie</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Provider</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Purpose</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Duration</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">_ga</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Google Analytics</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Distinguishes unique visitors</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">2 years</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">_ga_*</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Google Analytics</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Maintains session state</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">2 years</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Local Storage (Not Cookies)</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">We also use browser localStorage for:</p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li><code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">theme</code> — remembers your dark/light mode preference</li>
      <li><code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">xconvert-bookmarks</code> — your bookmarked pages</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">This data never leaves your device.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">How to Manage Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">You can control cookies through your browser settings:</p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings → Privacy and Security → Cookies</li>
      <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Settings → Privacy & Security → Cookies</li>
      <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences → Privacy → Manage Website Data</li>
      <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings → Cookies and Site Permissions</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">You can also use the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a> to prevent analytics tracking.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Essential vs Non-Essential</h2>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Essential:</strong> localStorage (theme, bookmarks) — required for the site to function as expected.</li>
      <li><strong>Non-essential:</strong> Google Analytics cookies — used for understanding traffic patterns. The site works fully without them.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Questions about our cookie practices? Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
